the inital damage of the spell) the spell is resisted, but if it goes through(its all or northing) then we would have a, lets say an &quot;big&quot; icicle landing down every six seconds for 24 seconds. Now what actually causes the dot effect isn't the issue(i know big icicle is corney, just thinking top of my head) but i think it could work quite well. It gives wizards some substained damage. Now maybe we have just cold and fire versions and get 1 cold ever other rank and fire every other rank opposite cold.<br>
<br>
I would not think this would take away from a roleplay aspect. Is it unlikely that i could not quickly cast some &quot;fireballs.&quot; it just makes less micro management and less aggro.<br>
<br>
Now fire and cold could not stack(seems obvious) which would mean that we could not be &quot;masters&quot; of dot's. And they would rival that of &quot;doting classes.&quot; but could be a valuable spell.<br>
<br>
Well I am getting tired already, if i can think of anything to add to what i already have i will add it at another time. Please tell me what you think, if something like this has already been posted could you please leave the link. Hope you like the idea and give it some though and your input.<br>
<br>
