ld be my answer, although pickup groups would be nice sometimes, i've now made alot of freinds and i can usually group with some of them, or i do a quest instead, or make cash till someone i know tells me &quot;hey there, what you up to,fancy forming a group?&quot;  <br>
<br>
I do however think the twinking issue needs to be sorted, it's simply not fair that wizards are totally lvl dependant where melees are not at all lvl dependant anymore, and the other thing that gripes is the deap red resistances, i should still be able to do some damage to a deap red, or else melees should not be able to hit them either, because the mobs agi is so high and they dodge their attacks all the time or something.  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=nepenthes>Nepenthes</A> at: 3/18/02 4:06:23 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/usnyine.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Snyine</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 24<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/25/02 5:32 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New(i think) Idea for Wizard Dot's</span><hr size=1> What we need would be a dot form of a nuke that goes off in pulses (not a rain type they can run out from under) on one targeted mob have it overwrite snare and root so its just for exp groups. Also have it with very low aggro and the spell effect should stop if we are hit or stunned.<br>
<br>
Also we should have a new group buff that turns everyones spells into lure based spell not just nukes but snares and roots as well. This spell would have normal based spells at the regular spell cost hitting for full damage this spell would also make lures hit at x 2 effect.<br>
<br>
Id also like to see a translocate effect shield that ports mobs out of mele range with a aggro wipe but have it cost alot of mana. lasting maybe 30 min but the mini banish effect is a proc shield .<br>
<br>
Maybe a wizard arch ablitity to resist summon by high level mobs have it cost a dot and it only blocks one summon each time.<br>
<br>
Another arch ablity that would be nice is self immunity to rains and ae nukes.<br>
<br>
Anther nice idea for a arch ablity is a disipline where the wizard cant be stuned while casting maybe lasting 30 sec. <br>
<br>
Also i was thinking that we need a increase buff line I was thinking a self buff that is a percentage reduction to elemental and magic based nukes. Shield of elemetal convergence reduces fire cold and maybe magic based attacks by 10% at level 1-20, 15% at level 20-30 , 31-40 20% and so on :P (maybe have the 10% of the damage thats blocked partly converted to mana for the wizard).<br>
<br>
<br>
Lastly as a wizard i would like the idea of a temporal effect spell line ( acts as a buff that alters time around the wizard <br>
effects would be as follows: mana and health regen effect x2, food consumption x2 or 3, stamina drain 5 a tick stamina goes to 0 a str drain starts, if the wizard runs out of food or water the spell will not regen mana or hp instead it will drain mana and HP)<br>
<br>
Clarvoiance- spell line have it act as a short duration tracking ability.<br>
<br>
Precognition- Identifys the targets spell weaks is to.<br>
<br>
Convey- (self only)a reverse coth type spell that will port you to a group members current location (in zone normal spell) out of zone arch ability. How many of you get tells for ports after your already grouped and hate reseting bind point to port pick up someone thats late to the raid then have to run 10 min to get back to the main group ( I know i do)<br>
